Revision history for Locale-Country-Multilingual

0.25     2014-08-22

- Moved to Dist::Zilla.

0.24     2014-08-18

- Updated to CLDR v25.

0.23     2009-04-15

- created fr.dat from CLDR sources, which handles bug reported by
  MIVKOVIC (RT 45031)

0.22     2008-12-30

- demonstrate the use of use_io_layer in SYNOPSIS
- add CLDR license
- again no code changes in this release

0.21     2008-12-29

- documentation of development path (Bernhard Graf)
- change from Module::Build over to Module::Install (Bernhard Graf)
- no code changes in this release

0.20     2008-12-29

- Incompatibility change: country2code() returns codes in capital
  letters as defined by ISO-3166 (Bernhard Graf)

0.11     2008-12-28

- skip tests for pod and use_io_layer for Perls < 5.8.0 (Bernhard Graf)
- new dat files: Afrikaans, Amharic, Arabic, Azerbaijani, Belarusian,
  Bulgarian, Bengali, Catalan, Czech, Welsh, Danish, Dzongkha, Greek,
  Esperanto, Estonian, Basque, Persian, Finnish, Faroese, Irish,
  Galician, Gujarati, Hebrew, Hindi, Croatian, Hungarian, Armenian,
  Indonesian, Sichuan Yi, Icelandic, Georgian, Central Khmer, Kannada,
  Korean, Lingala, Lao, Lithuanian, Latvian, Macedonian, Malayalam,
  Mongolian, Malay, Maltese, Burmese, Norwegian BokmÃ¥l, Nepali, Dutch,
  Norwegian Nynorsk, Polish, Pushto, Romanian, Russian, Northern Sami,
  Slovak, Slovenian, Somali, Albanian, Serbian, Swedish, Swahili,
  Tamil, Telugu, Thai, Tonga, Turkish, Ukrainian, Urdu, Uzbek,
  Vietnamese (Bernhard Graf)

0.10     2008-10-31

- fixed "use constant" to work with older Perls (Bernhard Graf)
- described language fallback mechanism (Bernhard Graf)
- no lowercased names from all_country_names() anymore (Bernhard Graf)
- documentation for all_country_codes() (Bernhard Graf)
- changed date format here to YYYY-MM-DD (Bernhard Graf)

0.09     2008-10-30

- added a DESCRIPTION (Bernhard Graf)
- "languages" cn and tw are now deprecated (Bernhard Graf)
- language names may be amended by a region (Bernhard Graf)
- renamed cn.dat to zh.dat and tw.dat to zh-tw.dat (Bernhard Graf)
- language loading fallback from "xx_YY" to "xx" (Bernhard Graf)

0.08     2008-10-28

- set explicit utf-8 encoding for POD (Bernhard Graf)
- try to fix cn.dat and tw.dat (Bernhard Graf)

0.07     2008-10-27

- added correct Unicode support (Bernhard Graf)
- updated and fixed some errors in country data files (Bernhard Graf)
- tie language data to the class, not the instance (Bernhard Graf)
- possibility to preload language files at compile time (Bernhard Graf)
- added method assert_lang() to check availability (Bernhard Graf)
- changed from hashes to arrays where possible (Bernhard Graf)
- documentation (Bernhard Graf)
- tests for new features (Bernhard Graf)

0.06     2008-08-11

- Thanks to Andreas Marienborg for Norwegian dat file. (Fayland Lam)

0.05     2008-05-23

- Thanks to michele ongaro for Japanese dat files. (Fayland Lam)

0.04     2008-05-22

- Thanks to michele ongaro for Italian/Spanish/Portuguese/German/French
  dat files. (Fayland Lam)

0.03     2007-12-21

- add tw.dat (Fayland Lam)

0.01     2007-01-13

- First version, released on an unsuspecting world. (Fayland Lam)

